by Mugi4ok

You are in a Really White Room.
You see a switch.
This is a room. It is called "Really White Room". Although at this point you can't agree with this description. You think "Extremely Dark Room" actually fits better.
> x switch

> x switch
That's a switch. Probably. You have no idea, what it does. So do I. Maybe try switching it on? I believe nothing bad happens. Probably.
> switch on switch

> switch on switch
Well, much better now
> e

> e

You are in an east.
You can see a freaking giant keyhole.
You can go west, north, east or south.
Eastern world. Not much to say... Matryoshka?

You should also know one thing. I don't know how exactly this place works. It has lots of different loot, but loot in eastern part of this place is know available just for anyone.
Somehow, this place knows where you are from, so you won't be able to get any loot if you are not from one distinct eastern part of Earth. Someone call it CIS. Sorry, nothing I can do about that.
But you are still able to take the adventure, no force will stop you from doing that!
> x freaking giant keyhole

> x freaking giant keyhole
Someone must have really bad sense of humour. I wish to take a look at the key that fits this keyhole...
