You are in a wild west.
You can see a message board.
You can go west or east.
You can see a bunch of people dressed like cowboys near a building called "Saloon". You may think: "Wait a sec, is it..?"

And what have you expected heading west? Japan? Of course it is the (in)famous Wild West!

12 Is Better Then 6
You might want to take a look at the message board near saloon.
> x message board

> x message board
Amongst numerous paper sheets you distinguish two messages worth you attention.
First one offers you to take part in the shootout tournament. How predictable. Is that all what people did while living in the Wild West - murdering each other? Ugh, how medieval...

Hey, entry is free for everyone! Where should we enlist?!
Gun Done
Second note, that pulled your attention says the following:
"We are the sons of Anarchy. We are the train to the better world. To get a boarding pass one should provide the proof of fighting the law".

Don't look at me, I don't know what that means either. Sounds creepy. And anarchical.
> w

> w

You are in a noir.
You can see a red scarf.
You can go east or north.
For what you can see you're in the middle of the street. Quiet street. Ominously quiet. Even for the night.
And everything seems to be so... ehm... faded or bleached? Only thing that is really bright here is a red scarf lying on the opposite side of the street. What is this place, a noir?..
Blackwell Bundle
You hear something south of you.
> x red scarf

> x red scarf
Unnaturally bright red scarf. Yep, this is deffinitely noir. I should say I'm surprised it is red by itself, not because it is all covered in blood. Would be much more dramatic and mysterious.
Oh, it is wrapped around something. It appears to be a... ridiculously huge key? Man, why would someone make a key that big?!
Well, I know it is heavy but I have a feeling we are going to need it later, so you have to take it with you. This is no casual quest where you can put the whole damn massive key in your pocket, you know.
Nope, it won't fit into your pockets, don't even tr... I said, don't try it!..
.. So, you're not only stubborn, but capable one, huh? Well, let's see how you walk around with this stuff in your pocket.
> look south

> look south
Two strangers are talking. You approach them silently and listen to their conversation. You imagine your self in a noir detective...
Calvino Noir
You got distracted, aren't you? While listening to their chit-chat one thing really caught your ear. It's an adress which you prefer to write down for some definitely inexplicable reason. Are you seriously playing a detective?..
