You are in a space.
You can go east or west.
SPACE! SPAAAAAACE!

Well, here we are. Future.
You may wonder "But I thought we were going to space, not to the future!". Why, what could be more future-like but space exploration, huh? I do believe future of mankind lies here, in boundless space of Universe. I really want it to be this way. When I was young I used to dream a lot about space. Now... Now I don't. I have no dreams, in fact. And that's sad. But, enough of that.

Sooo, about our plan... What exactly we are supposed to do once we get into space?..
Out There Somewhere
Oh, yeah, almost forgot. I think you might want to know that ship is broken. Good thing is that it happened not in the open space, so we can reach that planet over there east of us on a small cruiser from that spaceship. Bad thing - we still got to repair it.
